May 11 2002
-----------
 Build 46:
 ---------
 * FARMail sub plugin's language file extension is now *.fml.
 * RootKey for plugins is now FARMail\Plugins.
 * Scripts are now a sub plugin.
 + The scripts sub plugin menu is fully configurable (as in Active-Help).
 * Quote is now a script for scripts sub plugin and works with selection too.

 Script functions:
 + integer blktype() - return 0,1,2 for selection block types NONE,STREAM,COLUMN
 + integer blkstart() - returns selection block start line
 + integer selstart(integer i) - returns selection start for line "i" (as in FAR)
 + integer selend(integer i) - returns selection end for line "i" (as in FAR)
 + string usrinput(string title, string message, string init) - shows a dialog with
     title "title", a line of text set to "message" and an editable line initialized
     to "init". Returns the contents of the editable line or an empty string on cancel.
 * redirect(string str, integer how) - the best I could do to override FAR's bugs.
   If how is even then the str is taken as a directory where to create a file.
   If how is odd then str is taken as a file name to create.
   If how == (0 || 1) - text is redirect but nothing more happens.
   If how == (2 || 3) - text is redirected, the other panel shows the redirected file and it
                        is opened in another editor. (if the original is non modal)
   If How == (4 || 5) - text is redirected, the other panel shows the redirected file and the
                        original editor is closed without saving.
   So it can be used in two ways:
   1. A script file with only one function - redirect.
   2. At the end of any script. In this case the original file is also changed but you can
      quit without saving changes.

 + HeaderList class has grown bigger and scarier :) to allow having multiple line fields.
   Meaning that this:

    set %to% = totrtx@barak-online.net
    header X-My-Comment = %from%
    appendheader %to%
    appendheader Привет!
    appendheader Hello!
    header X-My-Notice = How
    appendheader do
    appendheader you
    appendheader do?
    header X-My-Last = Bye!
    appendheader Пока!

   will be sent as this:

    X-My-Comment: Alex Yaroslavsky <totrtx@barak-online.net>
      totrtx@barak-online.net
      Привет!
      Hello!
    X-My-Notice: How
      do
      you
      do?
    X-My-Last: Bye!
      Пока!
    
   Вроде как багов нет, пустые appendheader выкидываются.
 * reply.fms updated to use appendheader.

